name: midnight "stitches" jacket
description:
This is an unlined de-constructed jacket made from midnight linen/cotton and with a pocket using my "stitches" design with a barebones fabric button (a spare button is included).

Measurements:  Size S/M
                          Length from shoulder to hem - 75 cm

This a lovely free-form jacket and you can play with the neck by adding a brooch as a closure or by positioning the collar in different ways.

All barebones products are original designs, hand-screen printed/dyed/sewn. Only water-based eco friendly inks are used.

name: gunmetal "petals" jacket
